<item>
            <title>[LU-400] patch unroll can&apos;t handle empty commits</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-400</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The patch unrolling tool, build/extract_patches, currently will create an empty dpatch if a commit is empty.  This causes dpatch some heartburn, so just skip empty commits.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="11122">LU-400</key>
